{"id":"fb9736ee-38ac-473d-b141-edee3a495eb1","name":"Hades","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">My boy builds coffins, he makes them all day<br>But it's not just for work and it isn't for play<br>He's made one for himself, one for me too<br>One of these days, he'll make one for you<br>For you, for you, for you</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">💀💀💀</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">Hades (</span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/English\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">/ˈheɪdiːz/</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">; </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greek_language\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">Greek</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">: ᾍδης, </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romanization_of_Greek\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">translit.</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">&nbsp;</span><em><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">Hā́idēs</span></em><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">, </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Attic_Greek_language\" class=\"mw-redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">Attic Greek</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">: </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/Greek\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">[háːi̯dεːs]</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">, later </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/Greek\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">[háːdεːs]</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">), in the </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ancient_Greek_religion\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">ancient Greek religion</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\"> and </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greek_mythology\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">mythology</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">, is the </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/God_of_the_dead\" class=\"mw-redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">god of the dead</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\"> and the king of the </span></strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greek_underworld\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">underworld</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 72, 94)\">, with which his name became synonymous.</span></strong><br><br>💀💀💀<br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0d4aae3b-3672-4dae-b6bd-78ad2e094eb0_character-dionysus\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9672f807-eb43-466d-9acd-843d24a4fd57_character-ares\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"></a></p><p style=\"text-","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0d253f13-df52-42fd-8a32-7351636640a8_f46463fd-e688-48a2-b350-144224cf7377.webp","creator":"Chiimikyu","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🔮 Magical","⛪ Religion","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","💽 Music Mania"],"chats":166,"messages":417,"created_at":"2024-08-17T18:13:02.526611+00:00"}